    "abstract": "<jats:title>Abstract</jats:title>\n                <jats:p>\n                  COVID-19 is associated with lymphopenia and \u2018cytokine storm\u2019, but no information is available on specific cellular immune responses to SARS-CoV-2. Here, we characterized SARS-CoV-2-specific CD4\n                  <jats:sup>+</jats:sup>\n                  and CD8\n                  <jats:sup>+</jats:sup>\n                  T-cells in patients with acute respiratory distress syndrome. The spike protein (S) proved a potent T-cell antigen and specific T-cells predominantly produced Th1 cytokines. These novel data are important in vaccine design and will facilitate evaluation of vaccine candidate immunogenicity.\n                </jats:p>",
